-- CPC Pipeline Seeks to Borrow Up to $2 Billion, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 2012-02-10T04:53:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-10/cpc-pipeline-seeks-to-borrow-up-to-2-billion-vedomosti-says.html
Caspian Pipeline Consortium may get
as much as $2 billion from banks to fund expansion,  Vedomosti 
reported today, citing people it didn’t name.  OAO VTB, Russia’s state lender, will help to arrange the
loan, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
